-- Blowfish's Haysom Says Exclusive Product Helping Sales (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-10-09T13:34:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-09/blowfish-s-haysom-says-exclusive-product-helping-sales-audio-.html
Brenna Haysom, president of Blowfish,
says the exclusivity of her product, which is the first hangover
remedy approved by the Food and Drug Administration, is helping 
her secure sales accounts with vendors. Haysom talked to 
 Kathleen Hays  and Courtney Donohoe on "The Hays Advantage" on 
Bloomberg Radio on October 8, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 15:11
 